{"tid":1561752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"屯門客運碼頭男子上吊　昏迷送院","createTime":"2019-09-11T17:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T19:18:45.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e6c463cb69b4073437c8666b99e72d02379ccd6","tid":1561752,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:06:24.000Z","msg":"昨日(11日)晚上11時許，一名男子被發現在屯門湖翠路148號屯門客運碼頭吊頸。消防員到場將其解下，事主昏迷送院搶救，警員正調查其身份及輕生原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=y6uglPlKbSLkZz%2BcPL4okfMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=a128e3aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190912/mobile/bkn-20190912001831074-0912_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c2b3480584f91498d38505333a683f59e29cdb78","tid":1561752,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7